ge;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><font color="#0000ff">&nbsp;</font></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;<font color="#002cfd" size="4" face="Arial">MI ii 133/87; &nbsp; &nbsp;Dug 3096. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;29.5.mm. &nbsp; 6.2gm.</font></p><p><font size="4" face="Arial"><em>About Extremely&nbsp;Fine, even light brown patination.</em></font></p><!-- End Description AucLister --></font><br> 
 
